{"title_page": "Spit it Out (Solar song)", "text_new": "{{notability|date=April 2020}}\n{{sources|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|2020 single by Solar}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Stip it Out\n| cover      = Solar - Spit it Out.jpg\n| alt        = \n| caption    = Cover of the single\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Solar (singer)| Solar]]\n| language   = {{hlist|Korean|English|}}\n| released   = {{Start date|2020|04|23}}\n| format     = {{hlist|[[Compact Disc|CD]]|[[Music download|download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| recorded   = 2019 - 2020\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[K-pop]]\n| length     = TBA\n| label      = {{hlist|[[RBW (company)|RBW]]|}}\n| writer   = Kim Yong-sun - Kim-Do Hoon\n| producer   = \n| misc       = {{External music video|{{YouTube|79agYOEgKQk|\"Stip it Out\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Spit it Out'''\" ({{ko-hhrm|\ubc49\uc5b4|}}) is an upcoming debut single by South Korean singer [[Solar (singer)| Solar]]. It is set to be released on April 23, 2020 by [[RBW (company)|RBW]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Baek|first=Ji-eun|script-title=ko: [\uacf5\uc2dd] \ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \uc624\ub298 '\uc2a4\ud54f\uc787\uc544\uc6c3' \ubc1c\ud45c\u2026\uc194\ub85c \uc544\ud2b8\uc2a4\ud2b8 \ub3c4\uc57d|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=076&aid=0003558010|work=Sports Chosun|accessdate=April 23, 2020|language=Korean|date=April 23, 2020|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref> The music video will be released on the same day.\n\n==Background and release==\nOn April 10, RBW agency announced that [[Mamamoo]]'s [[Solar (singer)|Solar]] would be making her solo debut with single \"Spit It Out\" on April 23.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mengnews.joins.com/view.aspx?aId=3075941|title=Mamamoo\u2019s Solar set for solo debut|date=April 10, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|last=Yoon |first=So-yeon|work=[[Korea JoongAng Daily]]}}</ref> The first promotional teaser poster for the single was released on the same day.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=003&aid=0009808309|title=\ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \ub370\ubdd4 6\ub144\ub9cc\uc5d0 \uc194\ub85c\u2026'\uc2a4\ud54f \uc787 \uc544\uc6c3'|date=April 10, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|last=Lee|first=Jaehun|work=Newsis|language=ko|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref> The official artwork cover was finally revealed on April 13.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=312&aid=0000442309a|title=\ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \uac70\uce68\uc5c6\ub294 \ub9e4\ub825\u2026\ud0c0\uc774\ud2c0\uace1\uc740 '\ubc49\uc5b4'|last=Woo|first=Bin|date=April 13, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|work=TenAsia|language=ko|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref> On April 14, the first teaser photo and the intro teaser video were released through official [[Social networking service|SNS]] account.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0004191868|title=\ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \uc194\ub85c \ub370\ubdd4\uace1 '\ubc49\uc5b4' \ud2f0\uc800 \uacf5\uac1c...\ud654\ub824+\uac15\ub82c \ud551\uac70\ud301 \ud37c\ud3ec\uba3c\uc2a4|trans-title=Mamamoo Solar unveils solo debut song 'Spit' teaser ... gorgeous + intense fingertip performance|date=April 14, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|work=OSEN|last=Kyung|first=Jimin|language=ko|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=469&aid=0000487304|last=Kim|first=Hana|title=\ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \uac15\ub82c\ud568 \ud3ed\ubc1c \ud551\uac70\ud301 \ud37c\ud3ec\uba3c\uc2a4\u2026\u2018SPIT IT OUT\u2019 \ud30c\uaca9 \ucf58\uc149\ud2b8 \uc608\uace0|trans-title=Mamamoo Solar, Explosive Fingertip Performance\u2026 Announcement on the concept of 'SPIT IT OUT'|date=April 14, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|work=[[Hankook Ilbo]]|language=ko|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref> On April 15, the second teaser photo was revealed.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=421&aid=0004588177|title=\ub9c8\ub9c8\ubb34 \uc194\ub77c, \uccab \uc2f1\uae00 '\uc2a4\ud54f \uc787 \uc544\uc6c3' \ud2f0\uc800\uc774\ubbf8\uc9